normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"329cb85eb85a3f245bf96abb0b23d25e90b1af96","tid":200872,"uid":58530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T10:53:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去到都係掃街，上左去江島神社行個轉<br />\n<br />\n加左成隻龍蝦/八爪魚大仙貝嗰檔好多人排，但冇食到</blockquote><br />\n幾好食既 有時間可以排 我上次排左成個鐘<br />\n但食過一次就唔會想再排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺蝦味好食d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而男朋友鐘意個岩洞 佢話有d探險feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n你地係個邊住過夜定點?有無買車票?<br />\n因為我即日來回啊 搞到啲野勁麻煩<br />\nbtw 個間野係邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fff93f48d930e2a5beb77921e145da2d5a390dc1","tid":200872,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T10:55:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>去到都係掃街，上左去江島神社行個轉<br />\n<br />\n加左成隻龍蝦/八爪魚大仙貝嗰檔好多人排，但冇食到</blockquote><br />\n幾好食既 有時間可以排 我上次排左成個鐘<br />\n但食過一次就唔會想再排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺蝦味好食d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而男朋友鐘意個岩洞 佢話有d探險feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n岩屋同稚兒之淵好似幾有趣諗住去，但上次黃昏先去到，岩屋關左門"},{"pid":"ac3283782734e758a94ab443e0c51f8ff0c7c64c","tid":200872,"uid":8745,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T10:56:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O4ptPLs.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO4ptPLs.jpg&h=4c8f30cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回程係條橋度見到富士山個影<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862fd94a0d649f03394963ef307bd58fa92f2ae8","tid":200872,"uid":23124,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04