/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n江之島好似有好多站落車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你睇左地圖先<br />\n<a href=\"http://i0.wp.com/pride180.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/enoshima02.png\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fi0.wp.com%2Fpride180.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2013%2F10%2Fenoshima02.png&d=i%2FQ10njZfEvfzeNkfPb7d0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=039fa94e\" target=\"_blank\">http://i0.wp.com/pride180.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/10/enoshima02.png</a><br />\n<br />\n基本上水族館唔係江之島上面, 只係附近<br />\n江之島上面都無車站</blockquote><br />\n之前睇 好似話要行5分鐘 但已經唔記得邊個站落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw 唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7abc0d9d5d6c3d44dc495ff79761b4227180595e","tid":200872,"uid":35586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T13:42:48.000Z","msg":"早2日去左，睇唔到富士山，4點左右仲落埋雨，sea candle唔比上頂，係2樓隔住塊玻璃睇景硬係差咁d"},{"pid":"fcda209c1bbcaca812ef96d389839ef55d4eafce","tid":200872,"uid":58530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T13:44:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>早2日去左，睇唔到富士山，4點左右仲落埋雨，sea candle唔比上頂，係2樓隔住塊玻璃睇景硬係差咁d</blockquote><br />\n好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但值唔值得用一日時間去"},{"pid":"32b9b4eb9f012b9b2dfb3fad4fc7bebbac072c88","tid":200872,"uid":35586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T13:45:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>去到都係掃街，上左去江島神社行個轉<br />\n<br />\n加左成隻龍蝦/八爪魚大仙貝嗰檔好多人排，但冇食到</blockquote><br />\n幾好食既 有時間可以排 我上次排左成個鐘<br />\n但食過一次就唔會想再排<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我覺蝦味好食d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n反而男朋友鐘意個岩洞 佢話有d探險feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GY1Sixd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGY1Sixd.jpg&h=a32df508&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n好靚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 點去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n其實岩洞入面無咩野睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n沿住條路一直行到尾就去到架喇"},{"pid":"af664639ffa05e23b078b3a0b6b323f3213de35a","tid":200872,"uid":29017,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T13:46:00.000Z","msg":"一定要食白飯魚(魩仔魚) 日文:しらす !"},{"pid":"3db30242a520efde5540d6b456c050c900ce2d61","tid":200872,"uid":35586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T13:48:44.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>早2日去左，睇唔到富士山，4點左右仲落埋雨，sea candle唔比上頂，係2樓隔住塊玻璃睇景硬係差咁d</blockquote><br />\n好頹<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但值唔值得用一日時間去</blockquote><br />\n值得啦，如果好天既話個景真係好靚<br />\n入到個島好舒服，好撚過去淺草雷門果d集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7c9e5cd08dacd404387852fa0b2a80225af228f","tid":200872,"uid":38775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T13:52:04.000Z","msg":"生白飯魚飯正到仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"675b763d51ccd9100b7e18f7c6fafc7fff052a4b","tid":200872,"uid":35586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T13:52:34.000Z","msg":"如果淨係去江之島唔去埋鐮倉其實半日夠曬<br />\n晏晝去睇日落然後夜d入samuel cooking garden好撚正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n下次要揾日好天去多次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a6852a1006622d4fd69b50129d04d11806648d9b","tid":200872,"uid":59668,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T14:00:35.000Z","msg":"有睇男兒當入樽既記得去車站影相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n座觀光塔我覺得可以唔洗比錢入去<br />\n聽聞夏天個沙