\" />"},{"pid":"52b6676a6c3aef5eb630095e8e92c866e300adb0","tid":200872,"uid":58530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:29:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊自己一個去<br />\n諗住即日來回<br />\n一日江之島加鐮倉夠時間嘛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我問過人唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"24406d5525be8fa5702a202f635a72e6b97f214f","tid":200872,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:34:47.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>黎緊自己一個去<br />\n諗住即日來回<br />\n一日江之島加鐮倉夠時間嘛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n夠<br />\n<br />\n新宿出發，上午鐮倉鶴岡八幡宮、大佛&amp;長谷觀音，下午去江之島睇埋日落返新宿<br />\n調轉上午去江之島先都得"},{"pid":"ba85e8736c9a400da5e8c260f57f5ba052f92cc9","tid":200872,"uid":8745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:41:48.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>黎緊自己一個去<br />\n諗住即日來回<br />\n一日江之島加鐮倉夠時間嘛?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我問過人唔夠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n9點或之前新宿出發一定得，除非要去齊所有景點<br />\ne.g. 去埋圓覺寺/建長寺/由比濱玩水"},{"pid":"600455ca4925cb45547bd86bda23caee42b947ee","tid":200872,"uid":23124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-14T18:49:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>星期6日會唔會仆硬街 勁多人架? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n比平時多人就一定嫁啦 但無香港mk tst迫到行唔到囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd002932000808cfb18c5aec816126e45ec3519","tid":200872,"uid":3748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T05:05:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>其實江之島水族館係邊個站落<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 